    GET all notes: http://localhost:3000/api/notes
    GET a specific note: http://localhost:3000/api/notes/:id
    POST a new note: http://localhost:3000/api/notes (with JSON body containing title and content)
    PUT/update a note: http://localhost:3000/api/notes/:id (with JSON body containing title and content)
    DELETE a note: http://localhost:3000/api/notes/:id
     
    To test -> Run "npm test"